📺 HOW TO SPOT THE CHARACTER CHANGE BEFORE THE BIG MOVE

Changes in market behavior (“character change”) can create tactical trading opportunities, especially during volatile markets.

In this Short video, I go through several examples of how you can identify shifts in price action, relative strength, and key technical setups to generate short-term trades.

I cover:
– #Bitcoin $IBIT diverging from equity futures;
– The strength in Bitcoin translated into trading opportunities in crypto-related stocks like $COIN $HOOD;
– $PLTR showing a relative strength signal;
– $IGV showing a Red Dog Reversal and signaling a rotation;
– $AMZN entering a gap and holding above the pivot level triggering momentum.

